But when you try to remember
what used to be there,

545
00:25:15,947 --> 00:25:17,582
it's hard to recall.

546
00:25:19,451 --> 00:25:21,019
I'll watch your show when it airs.

547
00:25:21,086 --> 00:25:22,187
Thanks.

548
00:25:22,254 --> 00:25:23,788
-Excuse me.
-Uh-huh!

549
00:25:40,138 --> 00:25:41,473
