556
00:25:57,155 --> 00:25:58,390
Wait a minute, you two.

557
00:25:58,456 --> 00:25:59,824
You're formal with each other?

558
00:25:59,891 --> 00:26:00,892
Yes.

559
00:26:00,959 --> 00:26:02,627
I feel more at ease this way.

560
00:26:02,694 --> 00:26:03,862
Yes, same here.

561
00:26:04,629 --> 00:26:07,265
Now there are two people
who get on my nerves.

562
00:26:07,332 --> 00:26:08,466
Wait,

563
00:26:08,533 --> 00:26:09,801
