564
00:26:09,868 --> 00:26:13,338
We matched on the app
because we had similar preferences.

565
00:26:13,405 --> 00:26:15,674
I've never been in love
with anyone either.

566
00:26:15,740 --> 00:26:18,843
But I never have trouble
finding a sex partner.

567
00:26:19,844 --> 00:26:21,413
Why are you nodding, Akitsu?

568
00:26:21,479 --> 00:26:22,948
