569
00:26:23,014 --> 00:26:26,551
A meal partner, a sex partner,
a gaming partner…

570
00:26:27,052 --> 00:26:28,653
Having personal time is important.

571
00:26:29,154 --> 00:26:30,255
Oh, please.

572
00:26:30,322 --> 00:26:32,357
I'm starting to feel
like I'm the weird one.

573
00:26:33,458 --> 00:26:36,361
By the way, Ichiro, um…

574
00:26:37,429 --> 00:26:39,197
How long are you planning to stay here?

575
00:26:40,065 --> 00:26:41,366
As I've said,

576
00:26:41,433 --> 00:26:45,236
