606
00:28:07,952 --> 00:28:10,055
No, let's accept it.

607
00:28:10,121 --> 00:28:12,057
It was Four-Eyes being swanky.

608
00:28:12,123 --> 00:28:15,060
But the three of us
can't finish all of this.

609
00:28:17,429 --> 00:28:18,897
Why don't we invite those two?

610
00:28:20,131 --> 00:28:21,499
Is that so?

611
00:28:21,566 --> 00:28:23,401
So you're stepping in as Junko's mother.

612
00:28:23,902 --> 00:28:25,804
Just while Ichiro is away.

613
00:28:26,304 --> 00:28:27,138
How is she?

614
00:28:27,205 --> 00:28:28,840
Is Junko doing well?

615
00:28:28,907 --> 00:28:29,741
Yes.

616
00:28:29,808 --> 00:28:33,478
