00:28:43,922 --> 00:28:45,023
It's just…

624
00:28:45,090 --> 00:28:48,226
I can't tell if she's real or not,
if she's alive or not.

625
00:28:48,293 --> 00:28:49,728
It's so confusing.

626
00:28:51,162 --> 00:28:52,697
I wish I could cry too.

627
00:28:53,198 --> 00:28:54,733
I might never see her again.

628
00:28:57,502 --> 00:28:59,704
How was life back in the Showa era?

629
00:29:00,972 --> 00:29:03,842
Everyone talks about the good old days,

630
00:29:03,908 --> 00:29:05,343
but I'm not so sure.

631
00:29:05,844 --> 00:29:07,345
Because I wasn't born then.

632
00:29:08,880 --> 00:29:10,215
Let's see.

633
00:29:11,149 --> 00:29:13,718
