652
00:29:49,921 --> 00:29:52,724
Overall, it was quite noisy.

653
00:29:53,725 --> 00:29:54,692
You mean the streets?

654
00:29:55,226 --> 00:29:56,327
The construction?

655
00:29:56,394 --> 00:29:57,896
