656
00:29:58,696 --> 00:30:01,499
At the station or supermarket,
everyone was chitchatting away.

657
00:30:01,566 --> 00:30:04,702
Nowadays, people have this and this.

658
00:30:04,769 --> 00:30:07,772
They just look things up
instead of asking, so it's quieter.

659
00:30:09,941 --> 00:30:11,509
I've never considered that before.

660
00:30:14,045 --> 00:30:16,714
What about sexual or power harassment?

661
00:30:17,448 --> 00:30:18,349
Just terrible.

662
00:30:18,416 --> 00:30:20,952
It's so bad that
you have to numb yourself to it.

663
00:30:21,019 --> 00:30:22,420
No standards for identifying them either.

664
00:30:25,089 --> 00:30:27,759
A society that's a bit insensitive…

665
00:30:28,493 --> 00:30:31,462
might be easier for me personally.

666
00:30:37,235 --> 00:30:39,838
I don't think simply identifying
harassment helps, though.

667
00:30:40,939 --> 00:30:42,574
Labeling something as power harassment

668
00:30:43,074 --> 00:30:45,109
or moral harassment
instead of power harassment.

669
00:30:45,610 --> 00:30:47,011
By putting them into little categories,

670
00:30:47,579 --> 00:30:49,714
people feel like
they've addressed the problem.

671
00:30:53,284 --> 00:30:54,352
I see.

672
00:30:58,423 --> 00:30:59,991
I would've liked to go

673
00:31:00,959 --> 00:31:01,860
to Showa.

674
00:31:06,331 --> 00:31:07,999
That was yummy.

675
00:31:12,871 --> 00:31:13,905
Inoue,

676
00:31:13,972 --> 00:31:15,306
