677
00:31:15,807 --> 00:31:16,841
What for?

678
00:31:19,110 --> 00:31:20,778
Let's all go see Junko.

679
00:31:31,122 --> 00:31:33,224
INUSHIMA FAMILY'S GRAVE

680
00:31:33,291 --> 00:31:35,293
JUNKO INUSHIMA

